snippet.title: TV Schedule | Cartoon Network Show Listings
snippet.description: Find a complete schedule of local listings for all your favorite shows. Discover what to watch and when to find it on Cartoon Network.

snippet.title: Most Awesome Mascot - Rocky
snippet.description: The nominees for Most Awesome Mascot strut their stuff on the dance floor... Gangnam Style! Watch the Hall of Game Awards on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Undersea Town
snippet.description: Tom and Tub take the gang deep below Crystal Cove to a sunken city filled with German robots. Watch more Scooby-Doo! Mystery Incorporated on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: God of Destruction
snippet.description: Dynamis tells the legend of the five Blader Warriors who sealed away Nemesis, the god of destruction. Watch more Beyblade on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: LEGO Star Wars: Season 5 Episode 6
snippet.description: Count Dooku and General Grievous face the Jedi Council on Coruscant. Watch more LEGO Star Wars on Lego.com!

snippet.title: Level 6: The Final Boss
snippet.description: Harnessing the power of her gem, Amethyst defeats the evil Dark Opal. Watch more DC Nation on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Adventure Time - Pendleton Ward Interview
snippet.description: Adventure Time creator Pendleton Ward offers advice to young animators and challenges everyone to beat Righteous Quest in less than 6 minutes.

snippet.title: Cameron Audition
snippet.description: Meet Cameron, the genius "bubble boy," in his Total Drama audition video. Watch Total Drama Revenge of the Island, premiering Tuesday, June 5 at 7:30/6:30c on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Dragons - Catch a Glimpse
snippet.description: Be one of the first to catch a glimpse of DreamWorks' Dragons: Riders of Berk! Watch the series premiere Tuesday, September 4, at 7:30/6:30c on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Gumball's Wonderful Day
snippet.description: Gumball's day gets off to slippery start. Watch The Amazing World of Gumball Mondays at 7:30/6:30c on Cartoon Network
